  "texts": [
    "Another way to report findings is to determine \"true positives\" and \"true negatives\" for text passages that were AI-generated and human-written.",
    "In turn, these would permit calculating the true positive and the true negative rates.",
    "This is shown in Table 4.",
    "Using the numbers in Table 4, formulas (1) to (4) were used to calculate the numbers shown in Table 5.",
    "The calculation of true positive rates (TPR), true negative rates (TNR), positive predictive value (PPV), and negative predictive value (NPV) annuls the variance associated with only a few participants having assessed each passage."
  ]
}